start talking about the role that lighting played in pre-production and the work that

10
00:00:43,438 --> 00:00:45,219
was done that laid the foundation for the game.

11
00:00:45,979 --> 00:00:49,501
Then we'll dig into the really fun stuff of going through our artistic process and taking

