standing up one of the coolest levels in our game.

14
00:00:54,548 --> 00:00:57,670
And then we'll wrap up some insight

15
00:00:57,750 --> 00:00:59,332
on how we spent the final weeks of the game

16
00:00:59,432 --> 00:01:01,653
really diving into the nittiest of nitpicks

17
00:01:01,793 --> 00:01:03,274
to polish this product.

18
00:01:04,695 --> 00:01:05,676
But before we do any of that,

19
00:01:05,996 --> 00:01:07,197
let's do some quick introductions.

20
00:01:08,478 --> 00:01:09,398
My name is Brian Mullen.

21
00:01:09,418 --> 00:01:11,720
